Package: DCA_NMA
Type: Package
Title: Decision curve analysis for personalized treatment choice between multiple options
Version: 0.1.0
Author: Konstantina Chalkou, Andrew Vickers, Fabio Pellegrini, Andrea Manca, Georgia Salanti
Maintainer: The package maintainer <konstantina.chalkou@ispm.unibe.ch>
Description: Evaluation of an individualized prediction model in a network meta-analysis framework,
using an extended Decision Curve Analysis methodology.Decision curve analysis can be applied to 
network meta-analyses of randomized trials to evaluate whether the use of prediction models to aid 
treatment decision-making would do more good than harm.